## â“ FAQ

**Q: Works on all OS?**
A: âœ… Yes, Windows, macOS, Linux. Colors auto-disable if not supported.

**Q: Custom log format?**
A: ğŸš§ Currently `[timestamp] [LEVEL] message`. Customization planned.

**Q: Disable all logging?**
A: Wrap log calls in a condition.

**Q: Compatible with Pythonâ€™s built-in logging?**
A: âœ… Yes, itâ€™s standalone and non-conflicting.

